{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"70ddb1af8e","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"31d637ae6f","index":0,"year":1963,"month":3,"day":24,"articleId":"70ddb1af8e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"987425d21b","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，字停元，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。当时任湖南省副省长。"},{"id":"f29d0e2e52","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张千，字次卷，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时，他担任过该校校长。"},{"id":"41fa824041","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"应为张干的外孙女张琼英。"},{"id":"0a64ba82a0","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"蒋竹如，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。"}],"contents":[{"id":"59e32e89c0","type":"title","text":"给周世知的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e"},{"id":"987425d21b","type":"paragraph","text":"停元兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e"},{"id":"f29d0e2e52","type":"paragraph","text":"去年及今年惠寄数函并附诗词，都已收到，极为高兴。因忙退复，尚祈鉴谅。为学校题字，时间已过，可以免了吧。你到京时，我适外出，未能唔面，深致歉怀。-后如有所见，或有诗作，尚望随时见示为盼！老校长张干（忘其别甫，是否叫作次卷？）先生，寄我两信，尚未奉复。他叫我设法助其女儿以返湘工作，以便侍养。此事我正在办，未知能办得到否？如办不到，可否另想方法请你暇时找张先生一叙，看其生活上是否有困难，是否需要协助。叙谈结果，见告为荷。蒋竹如兄处，亦气见时代为致意。他给我的信都已收到了。顺问安吉","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e"},{"id":"41fa824041","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e"},{"id":"0a64ba82a0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六三年三月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e"}],"page":{"id":"0171c62b41","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"70ddb1af8e","start":371,"end":371}}}},"__N_SSG":true}